{"tid":1027931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國F－35B戰機在西太平洋首次投射「精靈炸彈」大秀軍事實力","createTime":"2019-02-19T06:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T00:47:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"80dda78d795aeda8e5d31fb753b7ed2316889b68","tid":1027931,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:46:15.000Z","msg":"美國F－35B戰機在西太平洋首次投射「精靈炸彈」大秀軍事實力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bf-35b%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E5%9C%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E6%8A%95%E5%B0%84-%E7%B2%BE%E9%9D%88%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88-%E5%A4%A7%E7%A7%80%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6%E5%8A%9B-045314589.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258Bf-35b%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B4%258B%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%258A%2595%25E5%25B0%2584-%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E9%259D%2588%25E7%2582%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25A7%2580%25E8%25BB%258D%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%258A%259B-045314589.html&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEpnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=6159b7eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bf-35b%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E5%9C%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E6%8A%95%E5%B0%84-%E7%B2%BE%E9%9D%88%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88-%E5%A4%A7%E7%A7%80%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6%E5%8A%9B-045314589.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國本周調派F-35和F-22隱形戰機、B-2隱形轟炸機在菲律賓和中國東海進行演訓，F-35B隱形戰鬥機還首次投射「精靈炸彈」，展現美軍堅強實力。<br />\n<br />\n《外交家》雜誌報導，根據美國印度太平洋司令部（U.S. Indo-Pacific Command）的一份聲明，本周在菲律賓和中國東海（西太平洋）的演訓當中，美國海軍陸戰隊的短距離起飛和垂直起降（STOVL）的超音速第五代F-35B隱形戰鬥機，從胡蜂號（USS Wasp LHD 1）兩棲攻擊艦起飛，並試射精靈炸彈（Smart Bombs）。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>F-35B戰機首次投射雷射和衛星導航的攻擊炸彈</strong><br />\n<br />\nF-35B戰機首次投下雷射導引炸彈GBU-12「鋪路」II型（Paveway II），以及衛星導航的GBU-32聯合直接攻擊炸彈（JDAM）。GBU 12和GBU 32為通用炸彈，重量分別為230公斤和460公斤）；F-35B戰機上還裝了CATM-9X空對空飛彈。<br />\n<br />\n「我們通過從胡蜂號戰艦起飛，與模擬敵機對戰，利用內部彈艙和外掛的精確導引炸彈，投彈打擊模擬目標，而後以垂直降落的方式返回「胡蜂」號戰艦，這是海軍陸戰隊第31遠征部隊的F-35B分隊第一次進行這一級別的作戰訓練。」「胡蜂」號F-35B分隊隊長朗特里（Michael Rountree）表示。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>F-35B於2018年9月首次在阿富汗支援攻擊行動</strong><br />\n<br />\n2018年9月，F-35B從阿拉伯海巡航的胡蜂級兩棲攻擊艦埃塞克斯號（USS Essex LHD 2）起飛，到達阿富汗進行第一次近距離空中支援攻擊行動，該戰鬥機外掛吊艙上安裝GBU-32聯合直接攻擊炸彈（JDAM）。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，據美國軍火商洛克希德馬丁公司稱，F-35B的單價最近有所下降，日本預計未來幾年內採購42架F-35B。<br />\n<br />\n「胡蜂」號雖為兩棲攻擊軍艦，卻有如一艘小型航空母艦，可以搭載31架軍用飛機，包括AV-8B「獵鷹II式」攻擊機、MH-60S「騎士鷹」（Knighthawk）直升機、AH-1Z Viper直升機和MV-22「魚鷹」（Osprey）傾轉旋翼戰機。 2017年，「胡蜂」號被改裝為能夠容納6架F-35B。"},{"pid":"284ad7f92243c8b3dbbd1f583f5bdcdb6470709e","tid":1027931,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b5fa758237a7740fd6c8f888c0fe28b4015842","tid":1027931,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:01:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8ab6fc939558aeeeda68b13f6f323aea72e750d","tid":1027931,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29b5fa758237a7740fd6c8f888c0fe28b4015842","tid":1027931,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:01:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:05:39.000Z","msg":"台灣 vs Chi-na 譯法"},{"pid":"04bb350409135606411747c1606cce79f2bfaf5e","tid":1027931,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073a4236cb2cec63d095be055f611941c3dc42a1","tid":1027931,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"射精  靈炸彈"},{"pid":"d6f732ccf2868b3b1dae33383af59b49c111e681","tid":1027931,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc